onMouseOut="nd();">
chap. 34</A>. For the "root of the reed" cp. <A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/1D*.html#80.5
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">chap. 80</A>, where the preparation


<A ID="p35x"></A>of such food is described. The <SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">corsaeon</SPAN> was the tuber of the Nile water-lily.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
