onMouseOut="nd();">34</A>
A far-fetched etymology: <SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">Dio-</SPAN> (from <SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">Dios</SPAN>, the genitive form of the nominative <SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">Zeus</SPAN>) and <SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">Nysus</SPAN> (<SPAN CLASS="translit_Greek">Nysa</SPAN>).


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
